OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 13 Jun to Sat 27 Jun
OL,6,FHigh pressure may become more dominant
OL,7,Fwith weather conditions becoming drier
OL,8,Fand more settled, although some
OL,9,Fshowery interludes are still possible.
OL,10,FTemperatures likely to trend above
OL,11,Faverage as we head further into June,
OL,12,Fwith very warm spells possible in
OL,13,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
